My meme section

This is a delicacy called Chuan Chuan Hot Pot from Sichuan, China. It is very famous in China and it is one of my favorite food. The soup is used to cook food and not to drink as it is too spicy.

Click here to get the restaurant address that I had the chuan chuan hot pot in New Zealand.

library(magick)

#Update the image
image1 <- image_read("https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/127640950/224522794-a1480939-bf26-4c5b-888a-40601e0ee87f.jpeg")

#Add an image to describe the image above
dem_image <- image_blank(width = 150, height = 300, color = "white") %>%
  image_annotate("Hot Pot!", color = "red", gravity = "south", size = 30)

meme <- image_append(c(dem_image, image1))

meme %>% image_write("my_meme.png")

My animated GIF section

This animation can be used for express love. Just send it to your sweetheart and express your love bravely! 

library(magick)

# First frame
frame1 <- image_blank(width = 300, height = 300, color = "purple") %>%
  image_annotate("L", color = "pink", gravity = "center", size = 70) %>%
  image_annotate("honey", color = "yellow", gravity = "southeast", size = 30, font = "mono")

# Second frame
frame2 <- image_blank(width = 300, height = 300, color = "blue") %>%
  image_annotate("O", color = "pink", gravity = "center", size = 70) %>%
  image_annotate("honey", color = "yellow", gravity = "southeast", size = 30, font = "mono")

# Third frame
frame3 <- image_blank(width = 300, height = 300, color = "black") %>%
  image_annotate("V", color = "pink", gravity = "center", size = 70) %>%
  image_annotate("honey", color = "yellow", gravity = "southeast", size = 30, font = "mono")

#Fourth frame
frame4 <- image_blank(width = 300, height = 300, color = "brown") %>%
  image_annotate("E", color = "pink", gravity = "center", size = 70) %>%
  image_annotate("honey", color = "yellow", gravity = "southeast", size = 30, font = "mono")

#Make them together 
GIF <- c(frame1, frame2, frame3, frame4) %>%
  image_animate(fps = 1)
GIF

image_write(GIF, "my_animation.gif")
